summary:
Expertise in Public and Developmental Policy, conducting qualitative and quantitative research, Diplomacy, International law, East Asian, European and African studies. Fluent in English, Intermediate in Korean and French. Experience in research organization, data analysis, qualitative and quantitative research, research communications  and academic writing. 
Diversity and Inclusion Ambassador.
